prompt:
Generate subtitles for the active timeline. Call `auto_generate_subtitles` with these arguments:

  target_language: {{target_language}}
  animation: {{animation}}
  max_words_per_chunk: {{max_words_per_chunk}}
  vad_sensitivity: {{vad_sensitivity}}
  highlight_color: {{highlight_color}}

Omit any argument whose value is empty or undefined. After the tool returns, summarize what was created (number of subtitle segments, language used, animation on/off) in one short sentence.
